      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just stuck in this same shitty cycle over and over. every time i think i finally got my life together, like i actually found a decent job or a stable routine, something just breaks and i end up right back at zero. it's like i'm just wired to fail. i'm so tired of trying to fix something that's fundamentally broken.",
