      "content": "it's just not working though. i'm not talking about burnout or needing more \"mindsets.\" i'm talking about the fact that the loop is inevitable. there's no \"different approach\" when the starting point is fundamentally flawed. it's like trying to fix a machine that was built to break. the only way to actually stop the cycle from repeating is to just make sure it can't ever start again. the loop only ends one way.",
